subject: Track and Field
Millrose Games
Pole Vault
Running
lead_paragraph: Bernard Lagat won the 102nd Millrose Games’ Wanamaker Mile in 3 minutes 58.44 seconds, tying Eamonn Coghlan’s record of seven titles.
